title: [Patreon Preview] Bean-Boozled
itunes:title: [Patreon Preview] Bean-Boozled
description:
On this week's after show, the gang talks about what three albums they'd bring with them to a deserted island and then play a good ol' game of bean-boozled, having eat jelly beans that could be tutti frutti flavored or it could very well be dirty socks flavored. They also ask adult film star Lexi Luna bonus questions that were not featured in the last podcast!
